  "doc_id": "33327",
  "text": "Roundness measurement will provide the deviation value or out-of-roundness from the real hemisphere radius based on the reference as a raw data. The output of roundness measurement consisted of a set of n numbers which represented the radial deviations of the workpiece at each point. Roundness profiles were transferred to the polar graph according to Spragg equation [CITATION_1] .",
